title: Talking Heads Live - Sydney 1979
description:
The Talking Heads, performing live at the State Theatre, Sydney, 8th June 1979. 

Recorded and miked professionally by government radio station JJJ. This rebroadcast was captured with a Yamaha component tuner to wav and encoded with LAME (q0, V1). An announcer talked or played the station logo between tracks 2&3, 5&6 and 7&8, but I cut these 'watermarks' out in a way that hopefully creates the feel of a seamless set.
 
Total length: 32 minutes 36 seconds

    Tracks:

          1. The Book I Read (4:42)
          2. Paper (2:35)
          3. Mind (4:23)
          4. Found a Job (4:51)
          5. Memories (3:44)
          6. Psycho Killer (6:02)
          7. Take Me to the River (6:19)
